@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ksdfxu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.cos((v0 + 0.17 / v1 + 0.90)))
    v0 = ((wp.abs(v1 + 0.04) - 0.53) * ((tmp + 0.33 - v1 + 0.97) + 0.40))
    v0 = wp.exp(v2)
    v0 = (wp.abs(wp.abs(tmp + 0.47)) * wp.cos(wp.abs(v0 + 0.11)))
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.sin(0.32))
    tmp = (wp.abs(0.45) + wp.sin(wp.cos(v0 + 0.84)))
    tmp = (v2 / tmp)
    tmp = v0
    data[tid] = v0
